==English==
===Etymology===
A post-classical Latin female form of classical Latin [[motor]] ‘motor’.

===Pronunciation===
[[IPA]]: /'məʊtɹɪks/

===Noun===
'''motrix'''
# a [[female]] instigator or [[cause]] of something
